            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Maternity Care</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Comprehensive maternity care is fully covered, including regular check-ups during pregnancy, the costs of childbirth (whether at a hospital, birthing center, or at home with a midwife), and postnatal care for both mother and baby. Importantly, <strong>no deductible or co-payment applies</strong> to maternity services.
            </p>
